ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Recommended for all interested in modern Chinese cultural history
Recommended for students who have basic understanding of modern Chinese history.

I would recommend this class to anyone studying China or history of science, as it appeals to a wide range of student audience. Knowledge of Chinese is not necessary, so I would recommend it to students outside of the department.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: enhanced my knowledge in late imperial Chinese cultural and technology history
Understanding of different aspects of language and script in China and in world history.
